body: league of legends has lost contact with maestro

replies.body: This maestro error could indicate an issue with your network connecting to the server.  Specifically, you can't establish a steady connection to group up with others into champion select.  I recommend following the steps in our [connection issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) guide to get this fixed up for good.  Hopefully this will get you fixed up, but hit me up if you have any questions!
